verbs.description: suny poly food service firm to [V: get] paid [ARG1: 55 000 for losses] the food service vendor at suny polytechnic institute in albany says it has lost so much money providing meals to suny poly students and staff that it wants to pull its operations from the high - tech school however officials with fuller road management corp the nonprofit that operates suny poly albany campus says it has reached a tentative settlement with the vendor chartwells that will keep it in place the deal involves a 55 000 payment to chartwells along with fuller road management agreeing to forgo 85 000 in commissions it would have earned over a two - year period going back to last year albany fuller road management corp 55 000 suny polytechnic institute chartwells suny poly doug grose albany new york fort schuyler fuller road management
